                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great introductory overview of an important subject</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
